abstract: Ligaya Mishan reviews Dawa's, Tibetan restaurant in Woodside, Queens.
lead_paragraph: At this Tibetan and American cafe, the thrill is the hidden tracks on the flip side of the menu.

headline.main: At Dawa’s in Queens, a Fusion of Earth and Sky
headline.print_headline: Where the Earth Meets the Sky
